EXPRESSION: CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Accounts Payable") + CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Short-Term Debt") + CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Long-Term Debt")
DIVIDE([Total Revenue] - [Total Revenue PY], [Total Revenue PY])

CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Vehicle Sales") +
CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Energy Storage Sales") +
CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Service & Other")

(
    CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Material Costs") +
    CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Direct Labor") +
    CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Manufacturing Overhead")
) * -1

[Gross Profit Calc]
- CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "R&D Expense")
- CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Sales & Marketing")
- CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "General & Administrative")
- CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Depreciation & Amortization")
- CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Interest Expense")
- CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Income Tax Expense")
CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Cash Flow from Operating Activities")

[Gross Profit Calc]
- CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "R&D Expense")
- CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Sales & Marketing")
- CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "General & Administrative")

CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "R&D Expense") +
CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Sales & Marketing") +
CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "General & Administrative")
CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Cash Flow from Operating Activities")
CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Cash Flow from Investing Activities")
CALCULATE([Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Cash Flow from Financing Activities")

IF (
    ISINSCOPE ( 'P&L Structure'[P&L Line] ),
    // IF TRUE (we are on a detail row), run original SWITCH logic
    VAR CurrentLine = SELECTEDVALUE ( 'P&L Structure'[P&L Line] )
    RETURN
        SWITCH (
            TRUE (),
            CurrentLine = "Vehicle Sales", [Vehicle Sales],
            CurrentLine = "Energy Storage Sales", [Energy Storage Sales],
            CurrentLine = "Service & Other", [Service & Other Revenue],
            CurrentLine = "Total Revenue", [Total Revenue Calc],
            CurrentLine = "Material Costs", CALCULATE ( [Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Material Costs" ),
            CurrentLine = "Direct Labor", CALCULATE ( [Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Direct Labor" ),
            CurrentLine = "Manufacturing Overhead", CALCULATE ( [Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Manufacturing Overhead" ),
            CurrentLine = "Total COGS", [Total COGS Calc] * -1,
            CurrentLine = "Gross Profit", [Gross Profit Calc],
            CurrentLine = "R&D Expense", CALCULATE ( [Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "R&D Expense" ),
            CurrentLine = "Sales & Marketing", CALCULATE ( [Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Sales & Marketing" ),
            CurrentLine = "General & Administrative", CALCULATE ( [Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "General & Administrative" ),
            CurrentLine = "Total Operating Expenses", [Total Operating Expenses Calc],
            CurrentLine = "Operating Income", [Operating Income Calc],
            CurrentLine = "Depreciation & Amortization", CALCULATE ( [Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Depreciation & Amortization" ),
            CurrentLine = "Interest Expense", CALCULATE ( [Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Interest Expense" ),
            CurrentLine = "Income Tax Expense", CALCULATE ( [Total Amount], 'public financialdataquarterly'[Account] = "Income Tax Expense" ),
            CurrentLine = "Net Income", [Net Income Calc],
            BLANK ()
        ),
    // IF FALSE (we are on the grand total row), return the base total amount measure.
    [Total Amount]
)

VAR CurrentActivity = SELECTEDVALUE ( 'CF Structure'[CF Activity] )
RETURN
    SWITCH (
        TRUE (),
        CurrentActivity = "Operating Activities", [Cash Flow from Operating Activities],
        CurrentActivity = "Investing Activities", [Cash Flow from Investing Activities],
        CurrentActivity = "Financing Activities", [Cash Flow from Financing Activities],
        BLANK()
    )
